{{Infobox company |image = File:HK Logo Wiki.png |name = Hard Knocks Fighting |type = Private |foundation = 2009 |founder = [[Ari Taub (wrestler)|Ari Taub]] |industry = [[Mixed martial arts]] promotion |location_city = [[Calgary, AB]] |location_country= [[Canada]] |key_people = [[Ari Taub (wrestler)|Ari Taub]], Founder and [[Chief executive officer|CEO]] | website = {{URL|http://www.hardknocksfighting.com/}} }}
'''Hard Knocks Fighting''' is a [[mixed martial arts]] (MMA) promotion in [[North America]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Hard Knocks Fighting Championship MMA Event will premiere on PPV|url=http://article.wn.com/view/2015/03/19/Hard_Knocks_Fighting_Championship_MMA_Event_will_premiere_on/|accessdate=5 July 2015|work=[[World News Network]]}}</ref> Hard Knocks Fighting was founded in 2009 by [[Canadians|Canadian]] Olympic wrestler [[Ari Taub (wrestler)|Ari Taub]].<ref>{{cite web|title=NATPE LIVE: Ari Taub, CEO of Hard Knocks Fighting, reveals news of a new 24/7 fight sports channel dedicated to content around its fighters and championship|url=https://www.natpe.com/blog/?p=3706|publisher=[[National Association of Television Program Executives|natpe]]|accessdate=5 July 2015}}</ref> Hard Knocks Fighting is known for its local fighter support and ongoing charity efforts and where [[Ronda Rousey]] secured her second career MMA victory.<ref>{{cite news|title=Local Calgary sports teams have netted nearly $100,000, thanks to Hard Knocks Fighting|url=http://www.calgarysun.com/2015/03/19/local-calgary-sports-teams-have-netted-nearly-100000--thanks-to-hard-knocks-fighting|accessdate=5 July 2015|work=[[Calgary Sun]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://themmacorner.com/2013/03/29/more-than-just-hockey-a-look-at-the-next-wave-of-canadian-mma/ |title=More Than Hockey: A Look at the Next Wave of Canadian MMA |publisher=Themmacorner.com |date= |accessdate=2015-03-12}}</ref>
==History==
===Founding=== In 2009, Canadian Olympic wrestler [[Ari Taub (wrestler)|Ari Taub]] founded '''Hard Knocks Fighting'''. [[Ari Taub (wrestler)|Ari Taub]] an Olympic wrestler and [[Calgary]] based lawyer overcomes local city bylaws to win legal challenges to get [[Mixed martial arts|MMA]] sanctioned in [[Calgary]].<ref>{{cite web|last=McAsey |first=Brian |url=http://www.ffwdweekly.com/news--views/news/political-cage-match-4438/ |title=Political cage match - Fast Forward Weekly |work=[[Fast Forward Weekly]] |date= |accessdate=2015-03-12}}</ref> In December 2011, media giant [[ESPN]] began airing Hard Knocks Fighting in 40 countries and over 50 million homes.<ref>{{cite web|title=HKFC School of Hard Knocks 36|url=http://espn.go.com/mma/fightcenter?eventId=400561074|publisher=[[ESPN]]|accessdate=5 July 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://www.mmacanada.net/2014/10/hard-knocks-39-takes-place-calgary-alberta-nov-14-special-guest-ufcs-elias-theodorou |title=Hard Knocks 39 takes place in Calgary, Alberta on Nov. 14 with special guest UFC's Elias Theodorou |publisher=Mmacanada.net |date=2014-10-21 |accessdate=2015-03-12}}</ref> Hard Knocks Fighting produces 15 live events annually, as well as shoulder programming including feature fights, highlight shows, and documentaries.
===Television Broadcasting=== * December, 2011 - Hard Knocks Fighting begins broadcasting on [[ESPN]].<ref>{{cite web|title=HKFC School of Hard Knocks 37|url=http://espn.go.com/mma/fightcenter?eventId=400595895|publisher=[[ESPN]]|accessdate=5 July 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=MMACanada |url=http://www.mmacanada.net/2014/10/hard-knocks-39-takes-place-calgary-alberta-nov-14-special-guest-ufcs-elias-theodorou |title=Hard Knocks 39 takes place in Calgary, Alberta on Nov. 14 with special guest UFC's Elias Theodorou |publisher=Mmacanada.net |date=2014-10-21 |accessdate=2015-03-12}}</ref> * June, 2013 - Hard Knocks Fighting begins broadcasting on [[Popcornflix]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.homemediamagazine.com/digital-evolution/popcornflix-stream-mma-action-30678 |title=Popcornflix to Stream MMA Action |work=[[Home Media Magazine]] |date=2013-06-14 |accessdate=2015-03-12}}</ref> * January, 2015 - Hard Knocks Fighting and [[MoboVivo]] launch HKFC MMA App <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportscastermagazine.ca/apps/mixed-martial-arts-app-hard-knocks-fighting-championship-mobovivo/1003406270/ |title=Hard Knocks Fighting Championship MMA App |publisher=Sportscaster Magazine |date=2015-01-15 |accessdate=2015-03-12}}</ref> * January, 2015 - Hard Knocks Fighting begins live broadcasts on [[Fight Network]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Quick Shots - Hard Knocks Fighting 43 LIVE on Fight Network|url=http://fightnetwork.com/news/56468:quick-shots-hard-knocks-fighting-43-live-on-fight-network/|accessdate=5 July 2015|work=[[Fight Network]]|issue=May 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pr.com/press-release/604006 |title=Fight Network Live Broadcast of Hard Knocks Fighting Championship |work=[[Home Media Magazine]] |date=2015-01-30 |accessdate=2015-03-12}}</ref> *
